info.title: Solartis Rate API for ISO-GL-V2
info.description:
To get rate for General Liability from Solartis Rate API with ISO ERC.
    General Liability Insurance is a business insurance policy that is
    applicable to most contractors and business owners because it protects them.
    When a business has this type of insurance policy, they're covered when it
    comes to claims of bodily injury, associated medical costs and damage to
    property that occurred as a result of your business operations.

post.description: Gets Rate for General Liability based on ISO ERC
